text: The Serbo-Croatian Wikipedia (Serbo-Croatian: Wikipedia na srpskohrvatskom jeziku, Википедија на српскохрватском језику) is the Serbo-Croatian version of the online encyclopedia, Wikipedia. There are also Croatian, Serbian and Bosnian Wikipedias. It is 19th largest edition by article count. == References == Category:Wikipedias
title: Serbo-Croatian Wikipedia
